<h2 class='page-intro'>A CES speaker is a thought leader, an innovative thinker and an industry influencer.</h2>
<p class="intro"><h3 style="margin-bottom: -5px;margin-top: -10px;">Important Dates</h3>

<p><strong>July 14:</strong>&nbsp;CES Call for Speakers closes<br />
<strong>Oct.&nbsp;12:&nbsp;</strong>Applicants notified of speaking status&nbsp;</p>

<h3 style="margin-bottom: -5px;">CES 2018 Call for Speakers</h3>

<p><strong>The Call for Speakers period is now closed.</strong> All applicants will be notified about their submission status by <strong>Oct. 12, 2017</strong>.</p>

<p><strong>Questions?</strong><br />
Please direct any questions regarding speaking at CES 2018 to the <a href="mailto:CESconference@CTA.tech">CES Conferences Team</a>.</p>

<h2><br />
Becoming a CES Speaker</h2>

<p>CES offers a variety of services for its conference speakers, including complimentary show registration.</p>

<h3 style="margin-bottom: -5px;">Speaker Guidelines</h3>

<ul>
	<li>Speakers cover their own travel expenses and hotel accommodations.</li>
	<li>Media and analysts have full access to conference sessions. There are no specific news services offered for speakers.</li>
	<li>The standard CES conference program formats include&nbsp;interview, fireside chats, presentations&nbsp;and moderated panel discussions.</li>
</ul>

<h3 style="margin-bottom: -5px;">Speaker Benefits</h3>

<ul>
	<li>Complimentary Deluxe Conference Pass, which include access&nbsp;the show floor, SuperSessions, keynote addresses, as well as nearly every conference track.</li>
	<li>Exclusive access to the Speaker Ready Rooms, lounge areas where speakers can fine-tune presentations and network with peers.</li>
	<li>Speaker Ready Room amenities include:
	<ul style="list-style-type:circle;">
		<li>Speaker work area/lounge space with light refreshments</li>
		<li>Computers with hardwired internet connection</li>
		<li>Wireless internet access for personal computers</li>
		<li>Printer and copier access</li>
		<li>CTA staff available to answer questions about CES and the conference program</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
</ul>

<h3 style="margin-bottom: -5px;">Expected CES 2018 Conference Themes</h3>

